# ============================================================
# FlagBridge Workspace — Inverted .gitignore
# Each subfolder is its own git repo. This repo only tracks
# the workspace scaffolding (setup, config, Claude agents).
# ============================================================

# Ignore everything by default
*

# ── Workspace scaffolding ──────────────────────────────────
!.gitignore
!README.md
!setup.sh
!flagbridge.code-workspace
!docker-compose.yml
!CLAUDE.md
!CONTEXT.md
!CONTROL.md

# ── Claude Code config ─────────────────────────────────────
!.claude/
!.claude/**

# ── GitHub org-level config ────────────────────────────────
# (the .github/ repo is cloned separately by setup.sh)
